pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$background"
elements:
  - elementId: header-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 50, 4, 30]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: header-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [76, 48, 200, 30]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>ABOUT US  //  من نحن</p>
  - elementId: title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 90, 600, 50]
    content:
      style: "$title"
      text: |
        <p>من نحن</p>
      wrap: false
  - elementId: body-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 160, 560, 140]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      text: |
        <p>Dealix هي شركة سعودية متخصصة في بناء أنظمة تشغيل الإيرادات المدعومة بالذكاء الاصطناعي. نساعد الشركات السعودية على تنمية إيراداتها وبناء ثقة عملائها والامتثال للأنظمة المحلية.</p>
  - elementId: mission-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 320, 120, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 2
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>MISSION</p>
  - elementId: mission-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 350, 540, 80]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: mission-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 362, 500, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "alimamashuheiti"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      text: |
        <p>تمكين الشركات السعودية من تحقيق نمو مستدام بالذكاء الاصطناعي</p>
  - elementId: vision-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 450, 120, 24]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 2
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>VISION</p>
  - elementId: vision-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 480, 540, 80]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$light"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "#E5E5E5"
  - elementId: vision-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 492, 500, 56]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$primary"
      fontFamily: "alimamashuheiti"
      lineHeight: 1.4
      text: |
        <p>أن نكون المنصة السعودية الأولى لإدارة الإيرادات والنمو</p>
  - elementId: side-image
    elementType: image
    bounds: [660, 90, 560, 580]
    src: "/mnt/agents/output/dealix-marketing/brand/executive-saudi.jpg"
    borderRadius: 4
  - elementId: side-overlay
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [660, 90, 560, 580]
    shapeName: rectangle
    fill:
      type: gradient
      colors: ["#1B5E3B00", "#1B5E3B88"]
      angle: 180
    borderRadius: 4
  - elementId: side-stat-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 580, 200, 20]
    content:
      fontSize: 12
      color: "#FFFFFF99"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      letterSpacing: 3
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>FOUNDED IN</p>
  - elementId: side-stat-value
    elementType: text
    bounds: [700, 604, 200, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 36
      color: "$white"
      fontFamily: "Liter"
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>2024</p>
